snippet.title: The Telwynium: Book One - Main Theme
snippet.description:
Recorded entirely with the classic Roland MT-32 synthesizer for maximum authentic retro PC game goodness. The Telwynium: Book One was a short adventure game developed for Adventure Jam 2021 by Powerhoof and took first place!

Download the game for free here!
https://powerhoof.itch.io/the-telwynium

Follow me on
Twitter: https://twitter.com/BrandonBlume
Soundcloud: https://soundcloud.com/musiclyinspired

Find more of my music at
http://brandonblume.com/
http://brandonblume.bandcamp.com/
